      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014I've babied it since day one! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
