      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered by a single owner, with a flawless exterior finished in a deep gloss that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no door dings, rock chips, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain supple with no bolster wear, and the original floor mats are in pristine condition. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean, fresh interior scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time at the dealership. The engine bay is detailed and clean, showing no signs of leaks or wear. It comes complete with two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and all owner's manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires zero investment\u2014just turn the key and enjoy.",
